divs: sighting detailswe went out side to smoke a cigartte & started looking at the stars when i noticed two areas; one stated flashing many different colors. the second was a pattern of rainbow like lights flashing in a disc like pattern. both areas moved very fast to very slow at times but they moved very violently about the area. at one point off in the distance i saw one come very close to the the ground & i saw what seamed to be a beam of light shine down on the ground below. however once again the object shot off directly up toward the sky. my fiance also witnessed the entire incident. at the very end of the incident we saw a greenish blue streak shoot off right over our heads the whole incedent we could not hear a thing everything was very quite. the whole incedent lasted about an hour-hour & fifteen minutes & acured around midnight. after all the above happend i witnessed\heard a low flying helicopter also fly across the area very low to the ground heading in the same direction as the lights we saw.
Summary: Many starnge lights & objects hovering & vearing across the Sky...
